    <h2 class="section-header">Why Choose Zipicka?</h2>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-4">
            <p class="lead paragraph-text">
                We understand that traveling can be stressful, especially when it comes to international travel. That's why we want to make your travel experience smoother and stress-free. At <span class="highlight">Zipicka</span>, our goal is to be your travel partner and make sure you have one less thing to worry about.
            </p>

